name: SHORELINE SECERTS BANGLE - TEAL COAST
description: Shimmer and shine with this extraordinary bangle with teal crystal balls accents and beads. Stack it up with some silver beaded bracelets or wear it alone for an elegant touch to any outfit. • crystal beaded balls and silver plated beads • adjustable to any wrist size • bracelet measures approx. 5cm in diameter Jewellery care It is recommended to avoid contact with water and moisture. If the piece gets wet, be sure to dry it off gently with a soft cloth or towel. Certain metals and plating can tarnish over time when exposed to elements such as pool and sea water, hair spray, perfume and lotions.

name: SPIKE YOUR STRIDE BRACELET - LAVENDER
description:
This bracelet has it all, spikes, chains and a pop of bright colour. Stack them up with beaded bracelets or wear them alone. Either way they're sure to add a spike to your stride.

• cotton duotone thread and gold plated spikes
• bracelet measures approx. 20cm
• gold metal plated adjustable chain 
• lobster claw clasp closure

Jewellery care 
It is recommended to avoid contact with water and moisture. If the piece gets wet, be sure to dry it off gently with a soft cloth or towel. Certain metals and plating can tarnish over time when exposed to elements such as pool and sea water, hair spray, perfume and lotions.
